  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>Release 02/16/2017 12:12PM CT (18:13 UTC)</p><h2 id=\"id-1.10.6-InventoryCountSheet\">Inventory Count Sheet</h2><p>The scan to count input is\u00a0not registering the &quot;enter&quot; key with\u00a0every scan (the enter key submits the scan entry). This is\u00a0an intermittent issue that affects some scans and not others, and it affects some barcode scanner models but\u00a0not others.</p><p>We added a few measures\u00a0to prevent this behavior for the troublesome\u00a0barcode scanner models. With this update scanning should work smoothly and consistently going forward for anyone who has experienced\u00a0trouble with this.</p>",
